Bates et al. (1999), Cooper et al. (2001), Findley (1972), Flannery (1995a), Han Naijian et al. (2010), Hill (1983), Huang, J.C.C. et al. (2014), Hutson, 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF346A8BF82B92AB1633BE39" box="[2007,2099,1266,1291]" country="Jamaica" name="Kingston" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">Kingston</collectingRegion>
&amp; Francis (2008d), Kitchener, Cooper &amp; Maryanto (1995), Kruskop (2013a), Smith &amp; Hood (1981).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
